snippet.title: Minigame Madness Launch Trailer - Play Now!
snippet.description:
Play NOW! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1408080?utm_source=YouTube&utm_campaign=LaunchTrailer

Minigame Madness is a frantic multiplayer party game where you compete against friends and strangers in a massive, ever-growing collection of unique free-for-all minigames to earn awesome loot and shiny badges!


Twitter - https://twitter.com/ChaoticDevs
Discord - https://discord.com/invite/BajtRQc
Website - https://MinigameMadness.net

Chaotic Entertainment is currently working on Minigame Madness, a frantic multiplayer party game where you compete against friends and strangers in a massive, ever-growing collection of unique free-for-all minigames to earn awesome loot and shiny badges!

Play NOW! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1408080?utm_source=YouTube&utm_campaign=LaunchTrailer
